shut down in 1878.

289
00:30:11,142 --> 00:30:14,680
Page 31, patient Edith Brennan.

290
00:30:24,155 --> 00:30:26,294
(GIRLS HUMMING EERILY)

291
00:31:21,412 --> 00:31:22,447
(SQUEALS)

292
00:31:29,320 --> 00:31:30,492
