All right, thank you, bud.

340
00:37:03,321 --> 00:37:04,595
Ma'am.

341
00:37:05,389 --> 00:37:06,868
Richmond's finest.

342
00:37:10,461 --> 00:37:13,465
Okay, guys,
just you and me for a while.

343
00:37:14,198 --> 00:37:19,477
I don't know how you're feeling about
that, but we don't got a choice.

344
00:38:08,486 --> 00:38:10,432
(EERIE MOANING)

345
00:38:15,393 --> 00:38:16,565
(MOANING GROWS LOUDER)

346
00:38:33,010 --> 00:38:35,115
DREYFUSS: How have they been
affected by all of this?

347
00:38:35,179 --> 00:38:37,022
ANNABEL: They are
talking to the walls.

348
00:38:38,816 --> 00:38:40,227
What do they say?

349
00:38:41,419 --> 00:38:42,727
Mama.

350
00:38:57,268 --> 00:38:58,611
What is this?

351
00:39:00,638 --> 00:39:02,208
They made that.

352
00:39:08,145 --> 00:39:09,317
(SHUTTER CLICKS)

353
00:39:12,650 --> 00:39:17,998
DREYFUSS: <i>They found a doll in the
cabin, Victoria. Who made the doll?</i>

354
00:39:20,925 --> 00:39:22,097
<i>Mama.</i>

355
00:39:23,594 --> 00:39:27,371
DREYFUSS: <i>The doll's called
"Mama," or Mama made the doll?</i>

356
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,240
VICTORIA: <i>
Mama made the doll.</i>

357
00:39:31,302 --> 00:39:32,872
<i>And who is Mama?</i>

358
00:39:34,739 --> 00:39:36,514
<i>Are you "Mama", Victoria?</i>

359
00:39:40,644 --> 00:39:42,021
(REWINDING)

360
00:39:58,095 --> 00:40:00,200
(PHONE RINGING)

361
00:40:01,198 --> 00:40:04,543
(ON VOICEMAIL) <i>This is Dr. Gerald Dreyfuss.
Please leave a message.</i> (BEEPS)

362
00:40:04,602 --> 00:40:08,982
LOUISE: <i>Dr. Dreyfuss, this is Louise
from Clifton Forge Public Records.</i>

363
00:40:09,039 --> 00:40:12,043
<i>Hound something that
you will want to see.</i>

364
00:40:30,795 --> 00:40:31,830
You guys okay?

365
00:40:49,246 --> 00:40:50,281
What's so funny?

366
00:41:10,601 --> 00:41:11,602
Good night.

367
00:41:12,403 --> 00:41:13,404
No!

368
00:41:16,073 --> 00:41:17,074
Whatever.

369
00:41:22,646 --> 00:41:24,216
Nice butt, Bruce.

370
00:41:50,074 --> 00:41:51,348
(WHINES)

371
00:41:59,783 --> 00:42:03,128
LILLY: (WHISPERING)
Victoria! Come. Mama.

372
00:42:06,824 --> 00:42:08,826
(EERIE HUMMING)

373
00:42:26,410 --> 00:42:28,390
