No fever, Doctor.

446
00:50:31,261 --> 00:50:33,070
DOCTOR: Mr. Desange,
can you hear me?

447
00:50:33,130 --> 00:50:34,734
NURSE: It's okay, Mr. Desange.

448
00:50:34,798 --> 00:50:35,936
(PANTING)

