496
00:53:23,700 --> 00:53:25,907
Outdoorsy.
You want coffee?

497
00:53:25,969 --> 00:53:27,175
Thank you.

498
00:53:30,340 --> 00:53:32,946
Oh, my God.
What is this?

499
00:53:33,977 --> 00:53:36,082
Yeah, I know,
they're wild sometimes.

